# immo server

this repo contains the basic idea of a simple sever that crawl https://www.immobilienscout24.de to get the latest offers.

### Features
- Crawls for new expose
- Crawl expose details page
- Send push notification

### Install
```
git clone git@github.com:pmdroid/immo-server.git
cd immo-server/
yarn
```

### Build
```
yarn build
```

### Create a user
Before creating a user you need to replace the credentials in the .env file
```
node dist/create-user.js
```

### Run
Before running you need to replace the credentials in the .env file
```
node dist/server.js
```